title: South Carolina man, 'gun hoarder,' had more than 7,000 stolen firearms, police say
text:
Published By: Al.com: Montgomery - Today 
Between 7,000 and 10,000 stolen guns were seized over the weekend at a Pageland, S.C. house and warehouse....
